We have rebuffed Hindenburg’s offer, dealing a serious blow to the nationalist-supported cabinet and shaking Hindenburg’s grip over the republic. Although we cannot topple Papen’s government just yet, our exclusion from the cabinet has brought its stability into serious doubt. The <span style="color: var(--dvp-color);">**[+ dvp_name +]**</span> has come far from its efforts at party reform, and as one of the few forces of the moderate right remaining, the Weimar parties look to us as a partner to protect the republic.

Democracy is on its knees, but we will help it stand up and fight.


@tolerate
subtitle: The republic is a sinking ship, but we cannot be a part of this sudden presidential cabinet.
view-if: dvp_ideology = "Right"
on-arrival: dvp_toleration = 1; dnvp_relation += 5 if dnvp_ideology = "Radical"; dnf_relation += 5 if dnf_formed; spd_relation -= 5; z_relation -= 5; ddp_relation -= 5; kvp_relation -= 5 if kvp_formed; dnvp_relation -= 5 if dnvp_ideology = "Moderate"; papen_coalition += dvp_r; workers_dvp -= 5; new_middle_dvp -= 3; old_middle_dvp -= 1; rural_dvp -= 1; dvp_toleration_papen = 1

Although Hindenburg would have liked for us to directly join Papen and work towards reshaping the republic into a more stable and autocratic state, he will accept our terms, as long as we promise to put our weight behind Papen. The situation is tense, the <span style="color: #954B00;">**Nazis**</span> and <span style="color: #8B0000;">**Communists**</span> have already infiltrated much of society, yet we have not been convinced of the potential <span style="color: #954B00;">**NSDAP**</span> taming project that a few on the right have put forward, with their vehement rhetoric and radicalism taking away from most hopes towards reconciliation. With the republic giving way, and Stresemann’s liberalizing influence on the party no longer tying us to the Weimar parties, our last remaining allies are the [? if dnvp_ideology = "Radical": <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> ?][? if dnvp_ideology = "Radical": <span style="color: #003755;">**DNF**</span> ?] and the various bourgeois parties.

[? if (dnvp_ideology = "Radical" and dnvp_relation > nsdap_relation) or (dnf_formed and dnf_relation > nsdap_relation): Even if our stance towards the <span style="color: #954B00;">**NSDAP**</span> was to change, we currently remain closer to the monarchists within the [? if dnvp_ideology = "Radical": <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> ?][? if dnvp_ideology = "Radical": <span style="color: #003755;">**DNF**</span> ?], and talks are already beginning about a joint list. ?]



@accept
subtitle: Caesar (Hitler) has risen from his grave, and we will do our best to tame him.
view-if: dvp_ideology = "Right"
